815
00:57:12,720 --> 00:57:14,260
- Thanks for taking care of the kids.

816
00:57:14,260 --> 00:57:15,173
- [Beth] Oh, sure.

817
00:57:16,834 --> 00:57:18,748
What about you?

818
00:57:18,748 --> 00:57:20,670
- [Sandra] What about me?

819
00:57:20,670 --> 00:57:22,223
- It's hard not to notice.

820
00:57:23,070 --> 00:57:23,920
Come on, give.

821
00:57:23,920 --> 00:57:26,823
- Oh no (laughs), it's that obvious?

822
00:57:29,460 --> 00:57:33,993
Well, um, Tommy is nice,

