00:58:24,370 --> 00:58:25,743
- Well, it's about Melissa.

836
00:58:27,380 --> 00:58:29,103
Did you ever have a thing with her?

837
00:58:33,323 --> 00:58:35,643
- Would it make any difference if I had?

838
00:58:37,974 --> 00:58:39,103
- Yeah, maybe.

839
00:58:43,720 --> 00:58:45,807
- No, Sandra, I never did.

840
00:58:49,475 --> 00:58:50,475
I never did.

841
00:58:59,487 --> 00:59:01,683
You're not gettin' cold
feet on me, are ya?

