00:59:04,950 --> 00:59:06,800
- Well, I guess this is it, isn't it?

843
00:59:27,960 --> 00:59:28,793
- You're late.

844
00:59:31,000 --> 00:59:34,083
Have a seat, I think
you're gonna enjoy this.

845
00:59:38,130 --> 00:59:40,030
- [Harris On Tape] Melissa
