855
01:00:28,050 --> 01:00:29,500
He never comes to the office.

856
01:00:31,190 --> 01:00:32,970
- It's not easy to get a grand jury

857
01:00:32,970 --> 01:00:35,183
to indict a public official like Caldwell.

858
01:00:36,810 --> 01:00:38,603
We only get one shot.

859
01:00:43,040 --> 01:00:46,590
Look, Tommy, I got a little something here

860
01:00:46,590 --> 01:00:47,790
that might help you out.

861
01:00:54,000 --> 01:00:57,430
The recorder fits in your boot.

862
01:00:57,430 --> 01:00:59,800
