01:02:48,240 --> 01:02:50,149
Here, I'm gonna get you nice and dry.

903
01:02:50,149 --> 01:02:52,580
- [Tommy] No, hey, hey, hey, it's fine.

904
01:02:52,580 --> 01:02:53,599
- Tommy, what is that?

905
01:02:53,599 --> 01:02:54,918
- [Tommy] Come on, here.

906
01:02:54,918 --> 01:02:58,168
(slow dramatic music)

907
01:03:01,494 --> 01:03:04,836
- [Sam] So thank you all
for your generous support.

908
01:03:04,836 --> 01:03:08,241
- Why Tommy I didn't
know you had it in you.

909
01:03:08,241 --> 01:03:09,360
- Uh, listen, I know you probably

