1000
01:12:01,640 --> 01:12:02,913
You're the key witness.

1001
01:12:03,940 --> 01:12:05,290
The hearing will be closed.

1002
01:12:06,730 --> 01:12:07,563
- [Sandra] And?

1003
01:12:09,330 --> 01:12:11,260
- Grand jury proceedings are secret,

1004
01:12:11,260 --> 01:12:12,630
no press, no public.

1005
01:12:12,630 --> 01:12:15,410
I can keep your involvement there hidden,

1006
01:12:15,410 --> 01:12:19,283
but if we get the
indictment against Caldwell,

1007
01:12:20,590 --> 01:12:22,373
you're gonna have to testify.

1008
01:12:23,940 --> 01:12:25,400
- In court?

1009
01:12:25,400 --> 01:12:26,463
- In open court.

1010
01:12:28,570 --> 01:12:30,343
- A grand jury can indict him,

1011
01:12:31,490 --> 01:12:33,543
but only a court can convict him.

1012
01:12:35,530 --> 01:12:37,363
It will be a public trial.

1013
01:12:41,340 --> 01:12:46,340
Look, I don't want you to put
yourselves in anymore danger.

1014
01:12:48,840 --> 01:12:51,823
I'll understand if you
choose not to go forward.

1015
01:12:54,629 --> 01:12:58,573
- (sighs) Look, I'm tired and I'm scared,

1016
01:12:59,490 --> 01:13:01,367
but I'm not about to back down now.

1017
01:13:06,960 --> 01:13:07,983
- Are you sure?

1018
01:13:09,170 --> 01:13:11,720
- Well, it's just a jailhouse rumor, Sam,

1019
01:13:11,720 --> 01:13:16,313
but the whisper is this is
going to the grand jury.

1020
01:13:17,770 --> 01:13:18,870
- Who's investigating?

1021
01:13:19,767 --> 01:13:21,467
Will you put that damn thing away!

1022
01:13:23,278 --> 01:13:25,410
- Well, I hate to be the one to say, Sam,

1023
01:13:25,410 --> 01:13:27,233
but it's the feds.

1024
01:13:28,990 --> 01:13:31,498
- It's that damn newspaper, isn't it?

1025
01:13:31,498 --> 01:13:34,800
- (coughs) I don't rightly know, Sam.

1026
01:13:34,800 --> 01:13:36,653
- Don't you Sam me!

1027
01:13:38,820 --> 01:13:41,821
Get off your fat butt and fix it.

1028
01:13:41,821 --> 01:13:43,280
- I can't do that, Commissioner.

1029
01:13:43,280 --> 01:13:44,730
- What do you mean you can't?

1030
01:13:45,850 --> 01:13:47,297
- Those Washington boys,

1031
01:13:47,297 --> 01:13:49,510
they're like mean ole ticks.

1032
01:13:49,510 --> 01:13:52,510
One smell of blood, they just
burrow right on in (chuckles).

1033
01:13:56,630 --> 01:13:58,393
- This isn't Washington, boy.

1034
01:13:59,830 --> 01:14:01,023
This is Georgia.

1035
01:14:02,538 --> 01:14:05,705
(slow delicate music)

1036
01:14:07,330 --> 01:14:09,530
- Listen, your mom
wanted me to talk to you.

1037
01:14:11,594 --> 01:14:13,540
(camera clicks)

