01:14:21,400 --> 01:14:23,203
You know these guys we work for?

1041
01:14:24,530 --> 01:14:26,363
Well, we've been trying
to put him in jail.

1042
01:14:27,560 --> 01:14:30,193
Now it's all about to hit the fan.

1043
01:14:30,193 --> 01:14:31,933
Things are getting a little,

1044
01:14:34,261 --> 01:14:35,511
well, a little dangerous.

1045
01:14:38,040 --> 01:14:40,593
- Is that why my mother sleeps
with a gun under her pillow?

1046
01:14:44,611 --> 01:14:47,278
(camera clicks)

1047
01:14:57,039 --> 01:14:59,956
- Well, we're working with the FBI.

1048
01:15:02,950 --> 01:15:04,820
I'm gonna have to testify
before a grand jury,

1049
01:15:04,820 --> 01:15:07,253
I might have to leave
town for a little while.

1050
01:15:10,637 --> 01:15:13,130
- What about my mom.

1051
01:15:13,130 --> 01:15:16,727
If you go away, she won't
have anyone, will she?

1052
01:15:18,786 --> 01:15:20,119
- Sure she will.

1053
01:15:22,144 --> 01:15:23,894
Someone real special.

1054
01:15:44,680 --> 01:15:46,130
- I'll be waiting right here.

1055
01:15:51,820 --> 01:15:54,213
- I promised Shane I'd take
him fishing this summer.

1056
01:15:56,140 --> 01:15:58,653
- I don't think Shane has
anything to worry about.

1057
01:16:02,640 --> 01:16:03,473
- [Tommy] Okay.

1058
01:16:16,520 --> 01:16:17,603
- There's all this food.

1059
01:16:18,560 --> 01:16:19,393
- [Tommy] Thanks.

1060
01:16:19,393 --> 01:16:20,226
- [Sandra] Mm hmm.

1061
01:16:20,226 --> 01:16:21,273
- Almost done, here it comes.

1062
01:16:24,090 --> 01:16:25,720
- [TV Reporter] Due to
unexpected rainfall--

1063
01:16:25,720 --> 01:16:26,553
- [Tommy] Where's Shane?

1064
01:16:26,553 --> 01:16:28,688
Shane, come on up, here it is.

1065
01:16:28,688 --> 01:16:30,271
Come on, hop along.

1066
01:16:32,620 --> 01:16:34,260
- [TV Reporter] And now here's Brian.

1067
01:16:34,260 --> 01:16:35,471
- [Brian On TV] On the local front,

1068
01:16:35,471 --> 01:16:37,870
a federal grand jury has indicted

